    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "2019 Honda Accord EX-L in fair condition. The engine and mechanical systems are functional but show some wear and may need minor repairs in the near term. The interior has visible wear, minor staining, and some cosmetic damage. The exterior has scratches and minor dents consistent with regular use. Overall a usable vehicle that will require some attention.",
